hkg抄1001呢個setting，咁改做1234至鎖post就冇問題？</blockquote></blockquote><br />\n唔好駁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你講嘅野真係好on9<br />\n你話isp mail emoji 乜乜台 1001其他forum都有<br />\n就好似話部部電話都有moon有開機制有音量制咁<br />\n係咪咁就代表小米唔係抄iphone?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家講緊lihkg所有野都係copy返高登wor<br />\n唔好駁啦照上咪算囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n照你咁講高登都係抄其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家都係抄<br />\n比乜野?</blockquote><br />\n好撚柒呀<br />\n高登除左emoji抄外國其他都係原創<br />\n你會唔會話iphone有mon an機有mon所以係抄嫁嘛<br />\n係樣樣都抄足好似小米咁先會話抄嫁嘛"},{"pid":"b0c31288b48334c27ff50ee67b18250c17dcb15d","tid":45251,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:24:28.000Z","msg":"格式排版一樣？你知唔知依家高登官方app係抄i2HKG同HKG+？自己對比返呢幾個app嘅上架同更新日期至好出黎廢嗡啦屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df721c45a137c716c3bc1ab019cec286d81b3da","tid":45251,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:32:32.000Z","msg":"就算係非官方web，同官方desktop web排版都好唔同，反而最近官方嘅M版web，就模仿得相當似我地呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b490c523442273e17e8866cf02fce7043d1ae7da","tid":45251,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T04:39:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n唔好駁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你講嘅野真係好on9<br />\n你話isp mail emoji 乜乜台 1001其他forum都有<br />\n就好似話部部電話都有moon有開機制有音量制咁<br />\n係咪咁就代表小米唔係抄iphone?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家講緊lihkg所有野都係copy返高登wor<br />\n